snippet.title: The Sims 3 Katy Perry's Sweet Treats Trailer
snippet.description: Indulge your Sims with the sweet and vibrant style of Katy Perry. The Sims 3 Katy Perry Sweet Treats pack showcases a vast range of décor items, furniture, and, of course, fabulous fashions and hairstyles! Inspired by Katy's real-life clothing and props, these fun furnishings, décor, and fashions will add a dash of sweet style to your Sims' lives.  It's bigger than a stuff pack and loaded with more content than ever before!
